A scalable and modular blockchain application built on Base, designed to enable secure, low-cost, and high-performance decentralized interactions.

This repository includes smart contracts, backend services, and frontend integrations for seamless Web3 user experience. The architecture follows best practices for security, gas optimization, and upgradeability.

Key Features:

- Smart contracts written in Solidity with full test coverage
- Integration with Base L2 for fast and low-cost transactions
- Modular and extensible architecture
- Secure wallet interactions (EIP-1193 compliant)
- CI/CD pipeline for automated testing and deployment

Tech Stack:
Solidity | Hardhat | TypeScript | Node.js | Ethers.js

This project aims to provide a production-ready foundation for building decentralized applications on Base.
